altername_name: Witch Rescue Service: Smoothly and with Style
name: Witch Rescue Service
overview: The preview was originally released for Halloween 2020, with updates released for each spooky season since. This good looking platformer was created by Carl-Henrik Skårstedt and the Space Moguls crew. A young witch has moved in to town and opened her missing persons rescue agency. Interesting cases await in this platforming escapade!
